'''距'''是某些植物的[[花被|花被]]（如[[风兰属|风兰属]]的距，[[堇菜属|堇菜属]]的[[花瓣|瓣]]距，[[凤仙花属|凤仙花属]]的[[萼|萼]]距<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2014/09/mystery-twisty-flower|title=The mystery of the twisty flower|author=Jia You|work=Science|publisher=AAAS|date=2014-09-08|accessdate=2021-04-14}}</ref>，[[翠雀属|翠雀属]]的萼距和瓣距<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Spurs in a spur: Perianth evolution in the Delphinieae (Ranunculaceae)|author=|url=https://www.journals.uchicago.edu/doi/10.1086/667613|last=Jabbour|first=Florian|last2=Renner|first2=Susanne S.|date=2012-11-01|journal=International Journal of Plant Sciences|issue=9|doi=10.1086/667613|volume=173|pages=1036–1054|issn=1058-5893}}</ref>）或[[被丝托|被丝托]]（如[[旱金莲属|旱金莲属]]的距<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Floral developmental evidence for the systematic relationships of ''Tropaeolum'' (Tropaeolaceae)|author=|url=https://academic.oup.com/aob/article-lookup/doi/10.1006/anbo.2001.1525|last=Ronse Decraene|first=L.|date=2001-11-XX|journal=Annals of Botany|issue=5|doi=10.1006/anbo.2001.1525|volume=88|pages=879–892}}</ref>）上形成的管状或囊状突起。<ref>{{Cite book|edition=第二版|url=https://www.termonline.cn/word/382905/1|publisher=科学出版社|location=北京|isbn=978-7-03-062178-8|oclc=1198145621|author=第二届植物学名词审定委员会.|title=植物学名词|year=2019}}</ref>大多数距内部有{{le|蜜腺|nectar}}，称为{{le|蜜距|nectar spur}}。亦有无蜜腺的距，如[[翠雀属|翠雀属]]植物的萼距。<ref name=":0" />

